title: Easy Star All Stars - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Easy Star All‐Stars performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded July 15, 2023

Songs:
Moonage Daydream
Ziggy Stardust
Suffragette City
Karma Police

Ras Droppa - Vocals, Bass
Joanne William - Vocals
JonnyGo Figure - Vocals
Andrew McIntyre - Guitar, Vocals
Horace James - Keyboards
Jenny Hill - Sax, Flute
John Speck - Trombone
Ivan Katz - Drums

Host: Kid Hops
Audio Engineer: Jon Roberts
Guest Audio Engineer, Audio Mixer: Nate Kipp
